svg.text: Only when I’m not in class can I come to your house to help you practice writing
过春节的时候，从农村到城市打工的人
過春節的時候，從農村到城市打工的人
Only during Chinese New Year can people from rural areas who work in the cities
go home to reunite with their children.
只有每天练球，比赛时才能好好儿
只有每天練球，比賽時才能好好兒
Only with daily practice can we perform well in competitions.
